Domo arigato to the Sony products, really.

88
00:04:38,203 --> 00:04:40,997
In fact, if you need someone
to eat some sashimi with you...

89
00:04:41,206 --> 00:04:42,749
...you give me a ring because...

90
00:04:42,916 --> 00:04:44,834
- Levison's right here.
- Write it down.

91
00:04:45,002 --> 00:04:47,754
I have to know that you're just seeing it.

92
00:04:48,380 --> 00:04:49,422
Good girl.

93
00:04:49,590 --> 00:04:51,340
Traffic from Malibu was impossible.

94
00:04:51,508 --> 00:04:53,301
- Morning, Joel.
- Morning, Celia.

95
00:04:53,469 --> 00:04:55,261
- Sandy, park the car, please.
- Okay.

96
00:04:55,429 --> 00:04:57,221
- Morning, Marty.
- Morning, Joel.

97
00:04:57,389 --> 00:04:58,765
Hi.

98
00:04:59,308 --> 00:05:03,728
- What are the Japs doing here?
- So, what's this talk about heads will roll?

99
00:05:03,896 --> 00:05:05,646
The bank's putting the screws to us.

100
00:05:05,814 --> 00:05:08,357
Harvey Goldman's son's coming out,
and I don't like it.

101
00:05:08,567 --> 00:05:12,236
Reggie Goldman's a pipsqueak.
You can't be serious.

102
00:05:12,446 --> 00:05:15,364
You know, some changes
are going on around here.

103
00:05:15,532 --> 00:05:19,368
It's always the way.
Happened at Paramount three years ago.

104
00:05:19,536 --> 00:05:21,412
Columbia's going through it now.

105
00:05:21,622 --> 00:05:23,706
I hear we're looking to replace Griffin.

106
00:05:23,916 --> 00:05:26,417
Griffin? I don't believe it. With who?

107
00:05:26,627 --> 00:05:28,544
Berg, Kirkpatrick. Maybe Larry Levy.

108
00:05:28,712 --> 00:05:33,424
Yeah. Yeah, well, I wanna know why
the security is so lax, that's why.

109
00:05:33,634 --> 00:05:36,511
I'll talk to you about it later.
I'm in the middle of a pitch.

110
00:05:36,678 --> 00:05:38,721
- Listen. Go ahead.
- Yeah, okay, okay.

111
00:05:38,889 --> 00:05:41,724
It's a TV star and she goes on safari
in Africa.

112
00:05:41,892 --> 00:05:44,227
You're talking about a TV star
